1
00:00:16,030 --> 00:00:18,290
It's the gun from the 8.17 Case, isn't it?

2
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:20,360
Is Zhou Jin working on this case?

3
00:00:21,010 --> 00:00:23,870
She's now responsible for
identifying the victim.

4
00:00:26,730 --> 00:00:28,410
Are you scared,

5
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:30,290
Officer Jiang?

6
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:10,620
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

7
00:02:10,940 --> 00:02:13,420
[Episode 4]

8
00:02:14,470 --> 00:02:15,380
I can see that.

9
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,810
I know what you're trying to do.

10
00:02:19,460 --> 00:02:20,020
Really,

11
00:02:20,290 --> 00:02:21,210
we were so close.

12
00:02:21,210 --> 00:02:22,270
Just a little more,

13
00:02:23,090 --> 00:02:24,930
and his mental defenses
would have been broken.

14
00:02:24,930 --> 00:02:26,050
Think about it.

15
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:28,310
Someone who can get a gun

16
00:02:28,780 --> 00:02:30,180
can't be a nobody, right?

17
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:35,140
Handling a case is never smooth sailing.

18
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:36,860
It's not your first time.

19
00:02:37,730 --> 00:02:38,410
Alright.

20
00:02:42,550 --> 00:02:44,550
Are you planning to cry here?

21
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:48,670
Oh my.

22
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:51,570
That's a huge bump.

23
00:02:53,329 --> 00:02:55,460
Go to the infirmary and get it checked.

24
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,200
Let me try one more time, please.

25
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,110
Just one more time.

26
00:02:58,110 --> 00:02:58,910
Alright.

27
00:03:00,370 --> 00:03:01,530
Haste makes waste.

28
00:03:01,620 --> 00:03:02,710
It's such a pity!

29
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:03,300
Zhou Jin.

30
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:08,950
Don't get stuck in the 8·17 Case.

31
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:11,010
I understand how you feel.

32
00:03:11,510 --> 00:03:13,190
We've tried your plan.

33
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,100
Reality proves

34
00:03:15,050 --> 00:03:15,980
that this method

35
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:17,140
doesn't work.

36
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:18,720
Alright.

37
00:03:21,579 --> 00:03:23,579
Don't forget to go to the infirmary.

38
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,360
Pursuing like this is too dangerous.

39
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,329
We can easily crash.

40
00:03:45,329 --> 00:03:48,260
Let's set up a roadblock at the exit
to intercept him.

41
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,090
Let's go.

42
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:09,220
You drove out of town
as soon as you got in the car.

43
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:10,620
What are you trying to do?

44
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:11,760
He's operating without a license.

45
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,560
He felt guilty

46
00:04:12,660 --> 00:04:14,380
and thought you were here
to catch illegal cabs.

47
00:04:14,380 --> 00:04:15,910
We just want to ask a few questions.

48
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:17,200
You've delayed us for so long.

49
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:17,980
Sorry, sorry.

50
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:18,860
I didn't know.

51
00:04:18,890 --> 00:04:20,089
I seriously suspect

52
00:04:20,110 --> 00:04:21,190
you're involved in other cases.

53
00:04:21,190 --> 00:04:22,070
No, no.

54
00:04:22,210 --> 00:04:24,200
Officer, please don't joke like that.

55
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,200
Let me remind you.

56
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:27,610
On the night of July 23rd,

57
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:29,050
did you get a ride request

58
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:31,330
to go to the Tonghe riverside
in the middle of the night?

59
00:04:31,330 --> 00:04:32,940
The night of July 23rd?

60
00:04:33,990 --> 00:04:34,990
Think carefully.

61
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:38,540
To the Tonghe riverside
in the middle of the night?

62
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:39,180
Yes.

63
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,370
There was such a person.

64
00:04:40,370 --> 00:04:41,010
And then?

65
00:04:41,210 --> 00:04:43,020
And then I went at the agreed time

66
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,070
and drove to the Tonghe riverside
to pick them up.

67
00:04:45,070 --> 00:04:46,000
Did you get them?

68
00:04:46,170 --> 00:04:46,780
No.

69
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,940
I only saw the person who booked the ride.

70
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,570
The person who booked the ride?

71
00:04:50,570 --> 00:04:52,190
The one who booked wasn't the passenger?

72
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:52,659
Right.

73
00:04:52,970 --> 00:04:53,680
Was it a man?

74
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:54,420
Right.

75
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,730
Is this him?

76
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:00,730
No.

77
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:01,790
Look closely.

78
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,730
It's really not him.

79
00:05:04,830 --> 00:05:05,500
I'm not trying to criticize you,

80
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:07,060
but can you not answer only when asked?

81
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:07,860
Say a bit more.

82
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:09,940
I'm a bit nervous.

83
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,440
That night,

84
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:13,010
I drove to the Tonghe riverside.

85
00:05:13,010 --> 00:05:13,970
I kept waiting,

86
00:05:14,450 --> 00:05:15,430
but no one showed up,

87
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:17,610
so I called the person who booked the car.

88
00:05:17,610 --> 00:05:18,900
He was nearby.

89
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:21,780
When he came over,
he even took the suitcase out of the car.

90
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:23,610
He told me his sister
wasn't leaving anymore.

91
00:05:23,610 --> 00:05:25,340
Anyway, he looked quite young.

92
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:27,590
It wasn't the person in your photo.

93
00:05:27,610 --> 00:05:29,250
If I let you see this person again,

94
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:30,170
could you recognize him?

95
00:05:30,170 --> 00:05:30,850
Yes.

96
00:05:31,250 --> 00:05:32,780
That guy had bleached hair,

97
00:05:33,050 --> 00:05:34,510
so he's easy to recognize.

98
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:50,930
Bleach,

99
00:05:51,460 --> 00:05:52,590
you're lucky today.

100
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,780
You've met a good person.

101
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:56,460
Since this lady is so curious,

102
00:05:56,730 --> 00:05:59,130
you better answer her questions properly.

103
00:06:02,370 --> 00:06:03,660
It seems to be...

104
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:04,510
Number three.

105
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:05,690
What do you mean "seems"?

106
00:06:05,690 --> 00:06:06,490
Look closely.

107
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:10,490
Yes, that's right.

108
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,660
That's him.

109
00:06:12,660 --> 00:06:13,460
Number three?

110
00:06:13,530 --> 00:06:14,290
Yes.

111
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:18,220
Sir, your task is done.

112
00:06:18,250 --> 00:06:19,060
Come with me.

113
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:20,610
Goodbye.

114
00:06:28,220 --> 00:06:28,820
Zhao Ping.

115
00:06:30,150 --> 00:06:32,080
Come interrogate this guy with me.

116
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:32,680
Yes.

117
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:33,350
Sir.

118
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:37,700
Haven't you embarrassed yourself enough?

119
00:06:38,610 --> 00:06:39,140
Let's go.

120
00:06:51,170 --> 00:06:52,860
Mr. Wan, Liang, I'm heading out.

121
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:53,460
Okay.

122
00:06:54,420 --> 00:06:55,130
Want some?

123
00:06:55,370 --> 00:06:56,050
I can't eat.

124
00:06:56,580 --> 00:06:57,780
Is it from Chuanwang?

125
00:06:57,930 --> 00:06:59,290
Once I deliver the baby, I'm going to eat

126
00:06:59,290 --> 00:07:00,490
every dish at Chuanwang

127
00:07:00,490 --> 00:07:01,980
and all the junk food.

128
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,460
Just hold out a bit longer.

129
00:07:03,730 --> 00:07:04,460
Smells so good.

130
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:06,520
Let me smell it to satisfy my craving.

131
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:11,050
Zhou,

132
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:13,210
if you're sleepy, go get some rest.

133
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:14,930
I'm not sleepy.

134
00:07:15,780 --> 00:07:16,900
What do you mean you're not sleepy?

135
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:18,230
Why are you so stubborn?

136
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:19,690
Don't complain about my nagging.

137
00:07:19,690 --> 00:07:21,070
When I first joined the force,

138
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:22,470
I stayed up late too much,

139
00:07:22,490 --> 00:07:23,490
and as a result...

140
00:07:24,810 --> 00:07:25,940
I picked up smoking.

141
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:28,170
Now I can't quit even if I want to.

142
00:07:28,470 --> 00:07:29,670
You just got married.

143
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:31,130
What if you want a child,

144
00:07:31,130 --> 00:07:32,600
but your body can't handle it?

145
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,810
Does what I'm saying make sense?

146
00:07:33,810 --> 00:07:34,540
Does it?

147
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:35,800
If you won't think of yourself,

148
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,860
think of your future child,

149
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:37,810
okay?

150
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:38,659
Professor Jiang,

151
00:07:38,659 --> 00:07:39,790
you're here so late.

152
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:45,760
Cigarettes

153
00:07:46,210 --> 00:07:47,010
cause cancer.

154
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:49,190
You must never touch them.

155
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:51,420
Professor Jiang is here.

156
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,060
Everyone, look after him.

157
00:07:53,370 --> 00:07:54,430
I'm going to smoke.

158
00:08:02,170 --> 00:08:03,170
Where's Zhou Jin?

159
00:08:03,550 --> 00:08:04,140
Zhou,

160
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:06,060
your husband is here.

161
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:09,790
Why are you here?

162
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,070
So sweet,

163
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:14,500
bringing a love-filled meal late at night.

164
00:08:22,690 --> 00:08:23,460
We can eat it.

165
00:08:23,610 --> 00:08:24,940
Can't let it go to waste.

166
00:08:29,020 --> 00:08:30,020
Have some with us.

167
00:08:30,020 --> 00:08:30,610
No need.

168
00:08:30,970 --> 00:08:32,970
Watching you two is filling enough.

169
00:08:39,809 --> 00:08:40,320
Did you

170
00:08:40,820 --> 00:08:42,020
come here specially?

171
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:44,100
I cooked too much.

172
00:08:46,610 --> 00:08:47,410
Are you...

173
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:52,080
The AC is too high here.

174
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:53,620
It's making my head hurt.

175
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:54,360
A headache?

176
00:09:06,220 --> 00:09:07,980
Let's go to the dorm.

177
00:09:19,010 --> 00:09:19,460
Sis,

178
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:21,300
just watching is bad for you.

179
00:09:22,050 --> 00:09:23,250
Eat the food.

180
00:09:25,490 --> 00:09:26,950
Actually, there's no need

181
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:27,890
to cook for me.

182
00:09:27,890 --> 00:09:29,090
I'm not a picky eater.

183
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:30,520
I eat anything.

184
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,210
It's no trouble.

185
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:46,530
That's my brother.

186
00:09:49,530 --> 00:09:50,180
I know.

187
00:09:50,890 --> 00:09:52,550
How come you know everything?

188
00:09:53,530 --> 00:09:55,220
When you lived in Zhizi Alley,

189
00:09:55,250 --> 00:09:56,410
you barely went out,

190
00:09:57,650 --> 00:09:59,450
but you seemed to know everyone.

191
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:00,840
You have great memory.

192
00:10:14,530 --> 00:10:15,700
Now you can tell me

193
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:17,900
why you're like this, right?

194
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:20,860
This dish

195
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,580
is really good.

196
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:25,230
I haven't tried this one. Let me try it.

197
00:10:28,170 --> 00:10:29,500
It has kiwi in it, right?

198
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:30,680
Zhou Jin,

199
00:10:31,430 --> 00:10:32,890
don't change the subject.

200
00:10:34,850 --> 00:10:35,730
Migraine.

201
00:10:39,410 --> 00:10:40,100
Don't move.

202
00:10:53,730 --> 00:10:55,650
I'm fine. It's nothing.

203
00:10:58,050 --> 00:10:58,720
Who did it?

204
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:01,560
Lai San bumped into me.

205
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:03,120
You interrogated him?

206
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,550
I tried to provoke him.

207
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:06,600
Zhou Jin.

208
00:11:07,650 --> 00:11:09,640
You clearly haven't
been on the front lines, have you?

209
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,930
Anyone who has

210
00:11:10,950 --> 00:11:12,330
knows that this is a minor injury.

211
00:11:12,330 --> 00:11:14,020
It's no big deal, really.

212
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,040
I clearly told you

213
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:17,800
to inform Chief Tan first.

214
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,840
I was worried this would happen.

215
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,970
I don't understand.

216
00:11:21,310 --> 00:11:22,970
Yes, I was a little impulsive.

217
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:24,980
I tried to provoke Lai San.

218
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:27,100
But isn't luring him
to admit to his crime

219
00:11:27,100 --> 00:11:29,700
a perfectly normal
interrogation technique?

220
00:11:29,730 --> 00:11:31,410
But you knew full well this method

221
00:11:31,410 --> 00:11:32,740
would put you in danger.

222
00:11:32,890 --> 00:11:34,680
Is there any investigation
that isn't dangerous?

223
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,860
You are a psychology expert.

224
00:11:35,860 --> 00:11:37,060
You should know better than me

225
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:38,290
that in this situation,

226
00:11:38,290 --> 00:11:40,100
it's more appropriate for a woman to go.

227
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:41,490
Plus, we have history.

228
00:11:41,490 --> 00:11:43,580
There is no one on the whole squad

229
00:11:43,580 --> 00:11:44,580
more suitable for this.

230
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:45,910
And what was the result?

231
00:11:45,950 --> 00:11:47,260
That result is you got hurt,

232
00:11:47,260 --> 00:11:48,220
and he didn't confess.

233
00:11:48,220 --> 00:11:49,460
But I tried.

234
00:11:49,490 --> 00:11:50,490
I have no regrets.

235
00:11:56,130 --> 00:11:56,770
I'm sorry.

236
00:11:57,900 --> 00:11:59,140
I need to cool down.

237
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:35,980
No!

238
00:12:36,180 --> 00:12:37,010
Nobody move!

239
00:12:37,010 --> 00:12:38,010
Don't kill me!

240
00:12:38,380 --> 00:12:39,100
No!

241
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:40,740
No!

242
00:12:43,580 --> 00:12:44,680
Don't kill me!

243
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:52,150
Are you scared yet,

244
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:54,150
Officer Jiang?

245
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:29,610
I'm sorry.

246
00:13:31,490 --> 00:13:33,460
I had a bad attitude just now.

247
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,700
I didn't consider your feelings.

248
00:13:37,490 --> 00:13:38,410
Actually,

249
00:13:40,490 --> 00:13:42,150
you're just worried about me.

250
00:14:03,530 --> 00:14:04,180
Hansheng,

251
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:07,820
investigations and interrogations

252
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:10,280
are both duties
of a criminal investigator.

253
00:14:10,710 --> 00:14:13,510
Whether I can get something out of him
is one thing.

254
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:16,500
Whether I go interrogate him is another.

255
00:14:17,890 --> 00:14:19,010
I know today,

256
00:14:19,220 --> 00:14:20,490
he didn't admit it,

257
00:14:21,460 --> 00:14:22,790
but during the process,

258
00:14:23,010 --> 00:14:24,300
for a brief moment,

259
00:14:25,450 --> 00:14:26,880
he almost gave in.

260
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:28,940
Really, he was just one step away

261
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:30,100
from confessing.

262
00:14:45,010 --> 00:14:46,940
I have to get used to facing danger.

263
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:52,580
And you have to get used to
facing this side of me.

264
00:14:53,870 --> 00:14:55,730
Lai San is just a marginal figure.

265
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:57,490
In the future,

266
00:14:58,180 --> 00:14:59,720
there might be more dangerous things

267
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,520
I need to face.

268
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:02,710
I know.

269
00:15:04,170 --> 00:15:05,860
I'm just a rookie on this team.

270
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:07,950
There are many people

271
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:09,280
who are more experienced,

272
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,240
more capable,

273
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:11,400
and smarter than me.

274
00:15:12,970 --> 00:15:14,130
But the team is still willing

275
00:15:14,130 --> 00:15:16,390
to give me such trust and opportunities.

276
00:15:16,970 --> 00:15:18,570
I don't want to let them down.

277
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:21,500
Even if I must risk my life,

278
00:15:22,090 --> 00:15:23,130
I won't back down.

279
00:15:24,450 --> 00:15:26,310
This is not just for the 8.17 Case,

280
00:15:26,490 --> 00:15:28,090
nor is it just for my brother.

281
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:30,200
Do you understand?

282
00:15:38,610 --> 00:15:39,400
Hansheng,

283
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:41,580
you're trembling.

284
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:43,680
I'm sorry.

285
00:15:45,370 --> 00:15:46,830
I raised my voice just now.

286
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:50,330
Today

287
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:53,690
was the first time you yelled at me.

288
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:14,000
As expected of newlyweds,

289
00:16:14,850 --> 00:16:17,190
sticking to each other like glue.

290
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,210
Done interrogating?

291
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:24,880
Done.

292
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:28,240
Huang Song is much easier to deal with
than Lai San.

293
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,890
His real name is Huang Song.

294
00:16:32,020 --> 00:16:33,480
He dropped out of Haizhou Vocational
and Technical College

295
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:35,030
after less than a year.

296
00:16:35,270 --> 00:16:36,290
He's from a single-parent family,

297
00:16:36,290 --> 00:16:37,820
raised by his mother alone.

298
00:16:38,010 --> 00:16:39,080
During his school years,

299
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:39,930
he didn't get along well

300
00:16:39,930 --> 00:16:41,680
with his teachers or classmates.

301
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:43,080
His grades were also poor.

302
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,490
Probably because of this,

303
00:16:44,490 --> 00:16:46,600
he hated staying at school more and more,

304
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:47,930
and often skipped class

305
00:16:47,930 --> 00:16:49,530
to hang out with young thugs.

306
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:51,490
Later, he met Lai Zhengtian

307
00:16:51,770 --> 00:16:53,930
and started introducing young girls
to the nightclub.

308
00:16:53,930 --> 00:16:54,680
Over time,

309
00:16:54,900 --> 00:16:56,960
Lai Zhengtian took him in as a lackey.

310
00:16:57,500 --> 00:17:02,560
[2015]

311
00:17:10,349 --> 00:17:11,810
Hey, hottie, have a drink.

312
00:17:22,290 --> 00:17:23,000
Lai!

313
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:28,600
Your commission.

314
00:17:30,810 --> 00:17:32,400
This is too much, Lai.

315
00:17:32,670 --> 00:17:34,110
This money is nothing.

316
00:17:34,170 --> 00:17:36,100
Today's drinks cost over 100,000.

317
00:17:36,460 --> 00:17:37,070
Come!

318
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:40,480
Here's to you!

319
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:41,930
Lai, I'll drink to yoU!

320
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,280
Bro,

321
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:47,370
you know what's the most important thing

322
00:17:47,370 --> 00:17:48,830
for a man in this business?

323
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,410
I don't know.

324
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:53,170
It's...

325
00:17:54,900 --> 00:17:55,940
Face!

326
00:17:59,450 --> 00:18:00,130
Got it?

327
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:01,440
Got it, bro.

328
00:18:01,750 --> 00:18:03,860
From now on, you just stick with me.

329
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:05,660
This world will be ours!

330
00:18:07,930 --> 00:18:08,610
Lai,

331
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:10,670
let me toast you.

332
00:18:11,610 --> 00:18:12,090
Come on.

333
00:18:12,810 --> 00:18:14,080
I have high hopes for you.

334
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:14,940
Thank you, Lai.

335
00:18:18,110 --> 00:18:20,550
What was the relationship
between Meng Ling and Lai Zhengtian?

336
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:22,420
Meng Ling was one of Lai's girls.

337
00:18:23,230 --> 00:18:25,490
She was the most popular with the guests,

338
00:18:26,050 --> 00:18:27,310
but she wasn't honest.

339
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,680
She had dirt on Lai.

340
00:18:30,610 --> 00:18:31,410
Lai said

341
00:18:31,930 --> 00:18:33,060
she was a hot potato.

342
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:35,950
She needed to be dealt with ASAP.

343
00:18:37,130 --> 00:18:37,930
What dirt?

344
00:18:39,460 --> 00:18:40,190
I don't know.

345
00:18:40,620 --> 00:18:43,180
Did "dealing with her ASAP"
mean killing Meng Ling?

346
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:45,230
He didn't want to kill her originally

347
00:18:45,230 --> 00:18:45,900
because...

348
00:18:47,070 --> 00:18:48,330
Jiang Cheng came back.

349
00:18:48,870 --> 00:18:50,070
Lai was scared of him.

350
00:18:50,810 --> 00:18:51,810
He didn't dare to.

351
00:18:52,210 --> 00:18:52,940
Jiang Cheng?

352
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:54,600
Which Jiang Cheng?

353
00:18:55,260 --> 00:18:56,720
The one from Phoenix Fire?

354
00:18:56,930 --> 00:18:57,480
Yes, him.

355
00:18:58,490 --> 00:19:00,820
What does this
have to do with Jiang Cheng?

356
00:19:02,910 --> 00:19:04,870
Jiang Cheng is a very capable guy.

357
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:08,340
Actually, I only heard about it.

358
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,760
Boss He likes smart

359
00:19:10,780 --> 00:19:12,040
and efficient people.

360
00:19:12,630 --> 00:19:13,980
Boss He thought highly of Jiang Cheng

361
00:19:13,980 --> 00:19:15,850
as soon as he joined the company.

362
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:19,040
He took Jiang Cheng with him everywhere.

363
00:19:19,520 --> 00:19:21,110
But Jiang Cheng and Lai didn't get along

364
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:21,970
from the start.

365
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:25,150
They even fought a few times
over business.

366
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:26,610
Boss He saw that the two of them

367
00:19:26,610 --> 00:19:28,140
really couldn't get along.

368
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:29,810
So,

369
00:19:29,810 --> 00:19:33,010
he transferred Jiang Cheng
to a branch office out of town.

370
00:19:33,350 --> 00:19:34,510
Actually, Lai knew

371
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:37,280
Boss He was reluctant to let him go.

372
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:40,110
It's just because Lai is his cousin.

373
00:19:40,650 --> 00:19:41,650
Family, you know.

374
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:42,910
It's different.

375
00:19:43,280 --> 00:19:44,890
Then why did Jiang Cheng come back?

376
00:19:44,890 --> 00:19:46,490
Because he signed a big order

377
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,870
and became a Hengyun's hero,

378
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:51,330
so he was transferred back.

379
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:54,430
This Lai San
doesn't dare to touch Jiang Cheng?

380
00:19:55,470 --> 00:19:57,090
Lai's been having bad luck.

381
00:19:58,140 --> 00:19:59,200
He was afraid
that after Jiang Cheng's return,

382
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:01,460
he wouldn't be able to keep his position,

383
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:04,510
so he hasn't dared to
make a single mistake recently.

384
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:07,030
Would touching Meng Ling
be considered a mistake?

385
00:20:07,030 --> 00:20:08,270
How could it not be?

386
00:20:09,130 --> 00:20:10,930
Meng Ling used to be with Jiang Cheng.

387
00:20:10,930 --> 00:20:12,250
If Lai really touched her,

388
00:20:12,250 --> 00:20:14,160
Jiang Cheng would end him.

389
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:14,780
Explain.

390
00:20:15,050 --> 00:20:15,910
She was with Jiang Cheng.

391
00:20:15,910 --> 00:20:16,590
In what way?

392
00:20:17,630 --> 00:20:19,150
Just... that kind of way.

393
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:21,800
As lovers.

394
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:24,000
Go on.

395
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:25,550
Lai said

396
00:20:26,510 --> 00:20:28,420
Jiang Cheng used to be a cop.

397
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:31,560
If Jiang Cheng
really wanted to mess with him,

398
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:32,900
he might not be able to handle it.

399
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:35,100
You all know Jiang Cheng used to be a cop?

400
00:20:36,760 --> 00:20:37,280
Yes.

401
00:20:38,740 --> 00:20:41,600
I heard he was dismissed
for violating discipline.

402
00:20:42,080 --> 00:20:43,720
Later he followed Boss He...

403
00:20:46,320 --> 00:20:47,480
and went into business.

404
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:48,340
What business?

405
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,480
Making a gangster sound so nice.

406
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:51,520
A cop?

407
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:53,320
Don't dirty our name.

408
00:20:58,810 --> 00:20:59,560
Go on.

409
00:21:02,670 --> 00:21:04,430
Lai was afraid of Jiang Cheng,

410
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:07,040
so he promised to give Meng Ling

411
00:21:07,460 --> 00:21:08,810
a sum of money

412
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:12,040
as compensation for her hard work
over the years.

413
00:21:12,220 --> 00:21:13,750
Then he asked me to find a car

414
00:21:13,950 --> 00:21:15,750
and send her back to her hometown

415
00:21:16,210 --> 00:21:17,740
to settle the matter early.

416
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:19,940
You call shooting someone

417
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:21,350
"settling the matter"?

418
00:21:23,930 --> 00:21:26,660
That's because she was stupid
and had a big mouth!

419
00:21:27,040 --> 00:21:27,610
Lai just

420
00:21:27,610 --> 00:21:29,280
insulted Jiang Cheng a little.

421
00:21:29,280 --> 00:21:30,960
Usually, no matter how Lai punished her,

422
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,200
she wouldn't make a sound.

423
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:34,080
But he mentioned Jiang Cheng
and she went crazy!

424
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:35,740
Why did she favor Jiang Cheng?

425
00:21:37,580 --> 00:21:39,380
That's why I say she's stupid.

426
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:45,020
I want to eat steak today.

427
00:21:45,560 --> 00:21:46,100
How about it?

428
00:21:46,100 --> 00:21:47,300
That place is not bad.

429
00:21:56,060 --> 00:21:56,660
Meng Ling,

430
00:21:56,740 --> 00:21:58,600
I have something to do. I gotta go.

431
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:02,170
Not staying to chat?

432
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:07,850
Not bad, Meng.

433
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:09,950
You're almost becoming

434
00:22:10,070 --> 00:22:11,510
the top prostitute.

435
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:13,870
Where are you going?

436
00:22:14,360 --> 00:22:15,620
You still want to shop?

437
00:22:15,630 --> 00:22:17,350
You want to dirty up this mall?

438
00:22:19,350 --> 00:22:21,130
Are you something clean yourself?

439
00:22:21,130 --> 00:22:22,200
Talking back?

440
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:30,470
Jiang Cheng, are you crazy?
You dare hit me?

441
00:22:31,020 --> 00:22:32,880
What does this have to do with you?

442
00:22:33,130 --> 00:22:34,460
Who do you think you are?

443
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,720
I'm her man, okay?

444
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:42,790
She believed whatever others said.

445
00:22:44,410 --> 00:22:46,270
It was like that with Jiang Cheng,

446
00:22:46,650 --> 00:22:48,250
and it was like that with Lai.

447
00:22:49,130 --> 00:22:51,130
She believed whatever others said.

448
00:22:52,580 --> 00:22:54,310
Tell me how Lai San tricked her.

449
00:22:55,810 --> 00:22:57,810
Letting her go back to her hometown.

450
00:22:58,350 --> 00:22:59,610
Wasn't that just a lie?

451
00:23:00,450 --> 00:23:00,970
Sister,

452
00:23:02,120 --> 00:23:06,280
[July 23 22:28]

453
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:03,740
why aren't you at home?

454
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:06,070
I'm not.

455
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,750
The driver is here.

456
00:23:09,070 --> 00:23:10,640
How about I put your suitcase

457
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:11,570
in the car first?

458
00:23:11,570 --> 00:23:13,300
Is Lai San really letting me go?

459
00:23:13,370 --> 00:23:13,890
Really.

460
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,520
But Lai said

461
00:23:15,520 --> 00:23:17,650
you must bring what he wants

462
00:23:17,650 --> 00:23:20,050
and then we'll go to
Tonghe to meet with him.

463
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:21,970
Once he gets the stuff,

464
00:23:21,970 --> 00:23:23,370
he should let you go home.

465
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:25,340
He also asked me to tell you...

466
00:23:26,110 --> 00:23:27,270
Don't play tricks.

467
00:23:28,570 --> 00:23:30,300
Lai San has moments of fear too?

468
00:23:32,260 --> 00:23:32,790
Sister,

469
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:35,920
what dirt do you have on Lai?

470
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:40,170
It's better you don't know.

471
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:46,590
Actually, I'd really hate
to part with you.

472
00:23:46,670 --> 00:23:47,190
Really.

473
00:23:47,550 --> 00:23:48,280
To be honest,

474
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:49,800
among all these people,

475
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:52,460
you are the second person
to truly care about me.

476
00:23:52,480 --> 00:23:53,830
You call me your sister.

477
00:23:54,150 --> 00:23:56,010
It's only right I take care of you.

478
00:23:56,450 --> 00:23:57,480
I'm leaving soon.

479
00:23:57,800 --> 00:24:00,130
Before I go, let me remind you
of one thing.

480
00:24:00,870 --> 00:24:04,190
Go to school. Study hard.

481
00:24:04,220 --> 00:24:06,590
Stop hanging out with Lai.

482
00:24:06,930 --> 00:24:08,930
I've heard this so many times.

483
00:24:08,950 --> 00:24:10,260
Not this.

484
00:24:11,050 --> 00:24:11,940
Then what?

485
00:24:13,350 --> 00:24:14,480
Be nicer to your mom.

486
00:24:15,540 --> 00:24:16,940
If my mom were still alive

487
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:20,090
and saw me being bullied like this,

488
00:24:20,180 --> 00:24:21,640
she would be heartbroken.

489
00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:25,760
What's wrong?

490
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:30,480
But she must be blessing me from heaven.

491
00:24:30,890 --> 00:24:31,370
Otherwise,

492
00:24:31,370 --> 00:24:33,230
I wouldn't have had such good luck

493
00:24:34,140 --> 00:24:35,340
to meet Jiang Cheng.

494
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:38,230
Did you say goodbye to Jiang Cheng?

495
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:40,520
I saw him,

496
00:24:41,700 --> 00:24:43,560
but I didn't mention I'm leaving.

497
00:24:46,130 --> 00:24:47,720
I'm not worth him missing me.

498
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:49,370
Hey, what are you talking about?

499
00:24:49,370 --> 00:24:50,370
That's not true.

500
00:24:51,040 --> 00:24:53,440
Jiang Cheng will become better and better.

501
00:24:54,460 --> 00:24:55,660
I can't hold him back.

502
00:24:58,370 --> 00:25:02,060
Song, Lai San is unreliable.

503
00:25:03,210 --> 00:25:05,480
Something bad will happen sooner or later.

504
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:06,650
Working with him

505
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:08,810
is not as good
as working with Jiang Cheng.

506
00:25:08,810 --> 00:25:10,010
Keep my words in mind.

507
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:15,820
Later, we waited at the agreed place.

508
00:25:17,050 --> 00:25:18,650
It was drizzling that night.

509
00:25:19,450 --> 00:25:21,980
Meng Ling didn't arrive
until around 11 or 12.

510
00:25:22,620 --> 00:25:24,410
Lai was already impatient from waiting,

511
00:25:24,410 --> 00:25:26,390
and he was in a bad mood
after drinking some alcohol.

512
00:25:26,390 --> 00:25:27,260
So when he saw Meng Ling,

513
00:25:27,260 --> 00:25:29,370
he didn't give her a good attitude at all.

514
00:25:29,370 --> 00:25:30,300
Get to the point.

515
00:25:30,520 --> 00:25:31,700
What exactly was the reason

516
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:33,160
that made Lai San kill her?

517
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:36,260
Meng Ling was too defensive against Lai.

518
00:25:36,410 --> 00:25:37,330
She was afraid of Lai's revenge,

519
00:25:37,330 --> 00:25:38,200
so she didn't bring

520
00:25:38,200 --> 00:25:39,730
the things he wanted at all.

521
00:25:39,890 --> 00:25:41,090
She was thinking of handing them over

522
00:25:41,090 --> 00:25:42,490
after she returned home.

523
00:25:42,610 --> 00:25:43,930
Lai got angry when he heard this,

524
00:25:43,930 --> 00:25:45,850
and told her not to
do things the hard way.

525
00:25:45,850 --> 00:25:47,610
Meng Ling stopped being afraid
when she heard this,

526
00:25:47,610 --> 00:25:48,480
and threatened Lai,

527
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:50,330
saying she would give these things
to Boss He.

528
00:25:50,330 --> 00:25:51,650
Lai got even angrier when he heard this,

529
00:25:51,650 --> 00:25:53,000
and they started arguing.

530
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:54,800
The argument was pretty normal,

531
00:25:54,820 --> 00:25:56,280
but for some reason, they suddenly

532
00:25:56,280 --> 00:25:57,610
mentioned Jiang Cheng.

533
00:25:57,610 --> 00:25:58,370
You also know

534
00:25:58,370 --> 00:26:00,240
Lai already hated Jiang Cheng.

535
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,610
Lai said he would kill him,

536
00:26:01,610 --> 00:26:02,570
make him kneel in front of him,

537
00:26:02,570 --> 00:26:03,200
and kowtow to admit his mistake.

538
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,000
When Meng Ling heard this,

539
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,000
she got even angrier.

540
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:06,000
Since Meng Ling was angry,

541
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,170
she brought up

542
00:26:07,170 --> 00:26:08,260
Lai's past.

543
00:26:08,570 --> 00:26:09,410
What past?

544
00:26:17,810 --> 00:26:19,070
It was about a year ago.

545
00:26:21,170 --> 00:26:23,030
Lai's hand was broken by someone.

546
00:26:23,610 --> 00:26:25,650
He hates it when others mention it.

547
00:26:26,910 --> 00:26:28,860
Boss He wanted to help him get revenge.

548
00:26:28,860 --> 00:26:29,990
He wouldn't let him,

549
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:32,400
saying nothing happened that day.

550
00:26:33,240 --> 00:26:34,040
But actually,

551
00:26:34,040 --> 00:26:35,640
a lot of people know about it.

552
00:26:36,470 --> 00:26:37,310
And then?

553
00:26:37,980 --> 00:26:41,040
Then Meng Ling said something
even Boss He doesn't dare

554
00:26:41,510 --> 00:26:42,420
to mention.

555
00:26:44,090 --> 00:26:45,130
Lai exploded.

556
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:48,870
I knew people like you were unreliable!

557
00:26:47,390 --> 00:26:51,710
[July 24 00:16]

558
00:26:49,570 --> 00:26:51,330
If you don't hand over the stuff today,

559
00:26:51,330 --> 00:26:52,930
do you think you can walk away?

560
00:26:52,930 --> 00:26:54,530
Let me tell you this, Lai San.

561
00:26:54,610 --> 00:26:55,170
If I can't

562
00:26:55,170 --> 00:26:56,720
return to Honglian safely,

563
00:26:56,890 --> 00:26:58,220
you won't get the stuff.

564
00:26:58,280 --> 00:26:59,680
I'm being too nice to you.

565
00:27:00,170 --> 00:27:01,170
Save your breath.

566
00:27:01,700 --> 00:27:02,710
Where is it?

567
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,040
I don't have it on me!

568
00:27:05,300 --> 00:27:07,260
Did you give it to Jiang Cheng?

569
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:08,440
No.

570
00:27:09,130 --> 00:27:10,480
Just let me go,

571
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:11,980
