Yes.

853
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:57,000
Whether in age,

854
00:41:57,040 --> 00:41:57,640
personality,

855
00:41:57,640 --> 00:41:58,500
social status,

856
00:41:59,100 --> 00:41:59,910
Lai Zhengtian

857
00:41:59,980 --> 00:42:02,120
is far superior to Huang Song
in all aspects.

858
00:42:02,120 --> 00:42:04,780
And given Huang Song's
premature experiences,

859
00:42:04,900 --> 00:42:06,180
he is in a state of absolute obedience

860
00:42:06,180 --> 00:42:07,650
to Lai Zhengtian.

861
00:42:08,850 --> 00:42:10,050
When the dominant one

862
00:42:10,250 --> 00:42:12,360
is more inclined to flee quickly,

863
00:42:12,930 --> 00:42:13,850
and the subordinate

864
00:42:13,850 --> 00:42:15,080
can calm down first,

865
00:42:16,040 --> 00:42:17,520
propose a body disposal plan,

866
00:42:17,520 --> 00:42:19,560
and take the lead
in covering up the crime,

867
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:21,000
this is a typical conflict
between personality

868
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:22,670
and criminal behavior.

869
00:42:25,040 --> 00:42:26,370
Is it possible

870
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:28,440
for the accomplice to strategize

871
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:29,440
and take over?

872
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:31,780
Of course.

873
00:42:32,680 --> 00:42:33,740
But this situation

874
00:42:33,940 --> 00:42:35,320
stems more from the accomplice's worship

875
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:36,630
of the principal criminal

876
00:42:36,630 --> 00:42:38,030
or long-term obedience.

877
00:42:38,930 --> 00:42:39,790
In other words,

878
00:42:40,160 --> 00:42:42,040
they would take the initiative
to clean up the crime scene

879
00:42:42,040 --> 00:42:44,370
out of an absolute desire to protect them,

880
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:46,170
and may even cover up the crime.

881
00:42:47,080 --> 00:42:48,140
But think about it.

882
00:42:49,080 --> 00:42:51,770
If Huang Song really wanted to
protect Lai Zhengtian,

883
00:42:51,770 --> 00:42:53,040
why would he so easily

884
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:55,860
reveal Lai Zhengtian's

885
00:42:55,890 --> 00:42:57,220
entire murder process?

886
00:42:58,560 --> 00:43:00,090
Isn't this contradictory?

887
00:43:01,730 --> 00:43:04,250
Huang Song's description of the murder
and body disposal process

888
00:43:04,250 --> 00:43:05,180
is not credible.

889
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:07,120
Indeed.
